So we discussed open
strings, so let's

00:02:03.350 --> 00:02:05.136
go back to the open string.

00:02:05.136 --> 00:02:10.500
For the open string, say
after we fixed the [INAUDIBLE]

00:02:10.500 --> 00:02:14.537
to be flat, the
[INAUDIBLE] action

00:02:14.537 --> 00:02:15.870
can be written as the following.

00:02:25.190 --> 00:02:27.920
OK?

00:02:27.920 --> 00:02:30.020
So you can-- when
you get the-- when

00:02:30.020 --> 00:02:43.600
you obtain the equation
of motion for x,

00:02:43.600 --> 00:02:46.830
you will have
something like this.

