Let's look at the
simple case first.

00:11:30.310 --> 00:11:32.680
So is this notation clear?

00:11:32.680 --> 00:11:38.660
So again, I can do this on
the similar plots like this.

00:11:38.660 --> 00:11:45.140
So now horizontal axis
[INAUDIBLE] x 0 to p,

00:11:45.140 --> 00:11:49.750
and the vertical
