00:12:30.550 --> 00:12:33.816
So this p plus 1
free parameter here.

00:12:33.816 --> 00:12:35.040
OK?

00:12:35.040 --> 00:12:38.330
And so this is a p plus
1 dimensional surface

00:12:38.330 --> 00:12:40.130
in the spacetime.

00:12:40.130 --> 00:12:44.870
And this condition
means that the endpoint

00:12:44.870 --> 00:12:49.180
of whatever open string must
