00:29:09.860 --> 00:29:13.110
But then I can also
have an open string

00:29:13.110 --> 00:29:17.350
which goes from b to a, and
for open string from a to b.

00:29:24.710 --> 00:29:26.280
OK?

00:29:26.280 --> 00:29:28.430
